{"tid":2206252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香城文化局]集思廣益 — 邀請各位巴絲一齊編寫我城歷史 (1)","createTime":"2020-09-17T11:13:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T15:54:20.000Z","uid":52152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cc0291dcafb4844012ab452ccb9c13d95b6aaa24","tid":2206252,"uid":52152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T11:13:47.000Z","msg":"因為上一個post已經沉到落地心，所以重新再開過新post。 <br />\n[香城文化局]召喚所有本土歷史同埋語言好既巴絲<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2102657\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2102657</a><br />\n[香城文化局]集思廣益 &mdash; 邀請各位巴絲一齊編寫我城歷史<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2163414\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2163414</a><br />\n同第一次見到依個post既巴絲介紹下，我哋依個工作小組主要希望係政權未完全將歷史改寫之前，擺脫依家主流由大中華角度出發，將香港無限矮化既歷史；將香港真正既歷史，真正由香港角度出發講述。<br />\n依家歷史方面我哋會整體歷史同地區歷史兩邊一齊同步搞。而語文方面，我見已經有其他同路人做緊，所以暫時唔開始着。<br />\n<strong><ins>整體歷史方面：</ins></strong><br />\n我哋砌緊一條時間線，入面分左3個時段（史前~清朝、港英時代、九七後）、由４個大範疇&mdash;政制(司法／行政／立法）、對外（軍事／外交）、當時生活情況（居住環境、信仰）、社會狀況（經濟結構），配合當時既時空背景去講。有左個初步既大綱之後就我哋慢慢填返做一段文字。<br />\n<strong><ins>地區歷史方面：</ins></strong><br />\n除左整體歷史之後，其實每一個地區本身都擁有自己好獨特既歷史。如果將佢哋好好梳理同整合既話，可以令到當區既居民更容易敢認識一下自己住緊既地方，鞏固本土文化。<br />\n<br />\n最後既目的係希望利用整合出黎既資料去整類似以下既片，從而令更多人認識香港既歷史。<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fwgtYmkIdow\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfwgtYmkIdow&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNOHvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=6dec29a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fwgtYmkIdow</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n但係每個人對香港/當區既歷史都唔同既睇法，所以需要大家幫手集思廣益。如果巴絲有興趣一齊編寫既話，可以填下面既form<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n整體歷史<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/7vuxZWWzZQnD1KoZA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F7vuxZWWzZQnD1KoZA&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNOHvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=7fa46416\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/7vuxZWWzZQnD1KoZA</a><br />\n地區歷史<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/EMzGujrPR4egqq6L6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FEMzGujrPR4egqq6L6&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNOHvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=1e0b4d6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/EMzGujrPR4egqq6L6</a>"},{"pid":"a6ea3e6abedd8ba733a8d7a643480c3392747b84","tid":2206252,"uid":52152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T14:00:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0b51ba9e563ebeaadce313a516a6c676130b264","tid":2206252,"uid":52152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T11:57:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad2f169bb6733f28a3d8b6631a979c7b7b65be3","tid":2206252,"uid":52152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T15:49:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed4797c067c85ce91eca5ff9a3823f775b1ba3f8","tid":2206252,"uid":52152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T12:05:24.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83750c09533f66b574e11efd38289ac71748fde0","tid":2206252,"uid":223208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T15:54:20.000Z","msg":"推"}]}